nt\b0 \highlight\uc2  of fiscal austerity and political debate there is a unique opportunity to change the conversation on development," said \uc2 John J. Hamre\uc2 , CSIS president and CEO. "We will look to the Council to offer recommendations for an aspirational agenda focused on delivering healthier people, healthier communities, and healthier nations."\par \par \uc2 The council will publish a report along with policy recommendations in 2013 addressing some of the areas CSIS aleady has a record of research including development finance, public-private partnerships, energy trends, local sourcing, agriculture and trade.\par \par \uc2 In addition to Daschle, Fiorina, Prizker and Weber, the council includes:\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 Honorary Co-chair: Henrietta H. Fore, Chairman and CEO, Holsman International, and CSIS Trustee\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 R. Hunter Biden, Chairman, Rosemont Seneca Partners, LLC\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 Edward D. (Ned) Breslin, CEO, Water For People\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 \uc2 Helene D. Gayle\uc2 , President and CEO, \uc2 CARE USA\uc2 , and CSIS Trustee\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 Mark Green, Senior Director, U.S. Global Leadership Coalition\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 \uc2 John J. Hamre\uc2 , President and CEO, CSIS\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 Benjamin W. Heineman Jr., Senior Fellow, Belfer Center for Science and International Affairs, Harvard University, and CSIS Trustee\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 \uc2 E. Neville Isdell\uc2 , Former Chairman and CEO, \uc2 The Coca-Cola Company\uc2 , and CSIS Trustee\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 Farooq Kathwari, Chairman, President and CEO, \uc2 Ethan Allen Interiors Inc\uc2 .\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 Paula Luff, Vice President, \b \highlight22\uc2 Corporate Social Responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2 , \uc2 Hess Corporation\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 Theodore E. McCarrick, Archbishop Emeritus of Washington, and CSIS Counselor\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 Robert Mosbacher Jr., Chairman, \uc2 Mosbacher Energy Company\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 Andrew S. Natsios, Professor in the Practice of Diplomacy, Edmund Walsh School of Foreign Service, Georgetown University\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 \uc2 Beatriz Perez\uc2 , Chief Sustainability Officer, \uc2 The Coca-Cola Company\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 Katherine Pickus, Vice President, Global Citizenship and Policy, \uc2 Abbott Laboratories\uc2 , and Vice President, Abbott Fund\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 Josette Sheeran, Executive Director, UN World Food Programme and incoming Vice Chair, \uc2 World Economic Forum\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 Anne-Marie Slaughter, Bert G. Kerstetter '66 University Professor of Politics and International Affairs, Princeton University\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 Mark Suzman, Managing Director, International Policy & Programs, Bill & Melinda Gates Foundation\par \par \uc2 \u226\'00\'E2\u8364\'20\'AC\u162\'00\'A2 Carolyn Woo, President and CEO, Catholic Relief Services\par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b NS\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 cexla : \uc2 Legal Action - Executives | e1101 : 