FT articles and redistribute by email or post to the web.   \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b LP\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 Ernst & Young\uc2  Entrepreneur of the Year was founded in 1986. Since then it has expanded to 140 cities in more than 50 countries. Each year, awards are presented to a thousand of the world's leading entrepreneurs, who are all winners in their own right.\par \par \uc2 Apart from its truly global footprint, what makes the programme unique is that the awards are judged by the entrepreneurs themselves. It is a celebration of enterprise and the creation of wealth and employment, which, particularly in tough times, is critical for the health of the global economy.\par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b TD\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 The culmination of the 2012 programme saw 59 country winners representing 51 countries attend the 12th World Entrepreneur of the Year ceremony, which took place last Saturday in Monte Carlo. Past winners of the global award include Olivia Lum of Hyflux, Icap's Michael Spencer, Narayana Murthy, co-founder of Infosys Technologies, and \uc2 Guy Lalibert\u233\'00\'E9\uc2  of \uc2 Cirque du Soleil\uc2 .\par \par \uc2 So how do the judges crown just one world entrepreneur of the year?\par \par \uc2 Each country winner goes through to the global contest and is then re-evaluated by a separate independent judging panel, which is rotated annually.\par \par \uc2 Each judge receives detailed histories of the country winners and meets the finalists in formal interviews, as well as informal events to hear their stories. The panel then convenes to rate candidates for six traits:\par \par \uc2 \u9679\'25\'CF Entrepreneurial spirit: examples of perseverance and fresh thinking; how they have overcome obstacles;\par \par \uc2 \u9679\'25\'CF Financial performance: today and their past record; their strategies for long-term growth sustainability;\par \par \uc2 \u9679\'25\'CF Strategic direction: how they are turning their visions into reality; their goals for growth; how they differentiate themselves;\par \par \uc2 \u9679\'25\'CF Global impact: what the business's impact has been in terms of revenue, operations and influence;\par \par \uc2 \u9679\'25\'CF Innovation: whether entrepreneurs anticipate and embrace change; whether there is continuous improvement and innovation throughout the business;\par \par \uc2 \u9679\'25\'CF Personal integrity and influence: whether there is a culture of \b \highlight22\uc2 corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2 ; the business's impact on the \b \highlight22\uc2 environment\b0 \highlight\uc2 ; and whether the entrepreneur's efforts have resulted in improved quality of life in the wider community.\par \par \uc2 .......................................................................\par \par \uc2 Maria Pinelli\uc2  is global vice-chairwoman for strategic growth markets at \uc2 Ernst & Young\par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\