distribute by email or post to the web.   \par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b LP\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 China, India and Brazil have been the trendy destinations for MBA study trips - until now.\par \par \uc2 In December a group of students from Stanford Graduate School of Business made Antarctica their destination of choice. So novel was the idea that Stanford dean Garth Saloner decided to go too.\par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b TD\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 The aim of the trip was to investigate climate change and business issues around it, in an \b \highlight22\uc2 environment\b0 \highlight\uc2  that is being affected more than most. David Shackelton, a distant relative of Ernest Shackleton, the Antarctic explorer, was one of the student organisers of the trip and brought together speakers from industry and policy as well as climate activists to talk on the subject.\par \par \uc2 What the trip brought home most forcibly to him was that climate change is often difficult to take seriously because it cannot be seen on a day-to-day basis. "It is still very intangible," he says.\par \par \uc2 For Shackelton, one of the most compelling issues is that companies have to act. "A lot of these problems can be solved profitably. You can call it \b \highlight22\uc2 corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2 , but it also makes economic sense."\par \par \uc2 The students and the dean were blown away by their visit. "There, you really are out in nature. There are no people. There is no litter. The path [you follow] has been made by penguins, not by people," says Prof Saloner.\par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b NS\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 gclimt : \uc2 Climate Change | gcat : \uc2 Political/General News | genv : \uc2 Environmental News | gglobe : \uc2 Global/World Issues | gwea : \uc2 Weather\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b RE\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 braz : \uc2 Brazil | china : \uc2 China | india : \uc2 India | apacz : \uc2 Asia Pacific | asiaz : \uc2 Asia | bric : \uc2 BRIC Countries | chinaz : \uc2 Greater China | devgcoz : \uc2 Emerging Market Countries | dvpcoz : \uc2 Developing Economies | easiaz : \uc2 Eastern Asia | indsubz : \uc2 Indian Subcontinent | lamz : \uc2 Latin America | samz : \uc2 South America | sasiaz : \uc2 South